para_trans: Deputy Chief Minister (Shri. regarding the allotment of office hall to the Principal Secretary at the establishment of Eknath Shinde).
Government Decision No. Shakaja-1125 / Q. 03/2025 Niwas-1,
Reference: A.S.P. No. AEO - 1125/10/2025 Bhaprasse-1, d. January 7, 2025.
According to a semi-official letter. On the installation of Deputy Chief Minister (Late Shri Eknath Shinde)
The Principal Secretary is Shri N. Naveen Sona, Principal Secretary (2), Public Health Department.
Mantralaya, Mumbai-32 has been appointed. So Mr. N. Naveen Sona, Bhaprasse
Additional Chief Secretary (Services), Ministry Main Building, 6th Floor for office work.
Hall No. 2, adjacent to the hall, is being remodeled.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
